<!-- =================== R6 REPRODUCE BUTTON =================== -->
<h3>R6. Reproduce-this-result button</h3>
<p><b>What.</b> For any URL analysis or deep-search session, expose a "Reproduce" button. Backend re-runs the analysis with the <i>same prompt version + same retrieval strategy</i> as recorded in <code>claim_provenance</code> and returns the diff (calibration shifted, new sources, new indicator data). The strongest possible demonstration that the platform is what it says it is.</p>

